### Multi-Tenant SaaS — HTTP request examples
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools.

### ---
### Setup: create organizations (as super_admin)
### ---

### Create Acme Corp (triggers validate_org_creation: sets default plan to "free")
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Acme Corp"
}

### Create Widgets Inc on pro plan
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Widgets Inc",
  "plan": "pro"
}

### Create GlobalTech on enterprise plan
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "GlobalTech",
  "plan": "enterprise"
}

### Fail: duplicate org name (case-insensitive uniqueness)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "  acme corp  "
}

### ---
### Plan transition enforcement (enforce_plan_rules)
### ---

### Upgrade Acme Corp from free to pro
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations/{{acme_org_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "pro"
}

### Fail: skip from free directly to enterprise
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations/{{acme_org_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "enterprise"
}

### Fail: downgrade from enterprise to free
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/organizations/{{globaltech_org_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "free"
}

### ---
### Tenant A (Acme Corp, free plan) — project limit enforcement
### ---

### Create project 1 (validate_project: auto-fills created_by from JWT)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website Redesign"
}

### Create project 2
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mobile App"
}

### Create project 3
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "API Platform"
}

### Fail: project 4 exceeds free plan limit (max 3)
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Data Pipeline"
}

### Fail: duplicate project name within org
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Website Redesign"
}

### List projects — only sees Acme Corp's projects
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}

### ---
### Project status enforcement (enforce_project_status)
### ---

### Fail: non-admin tries to archive a project
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/projects/{{acme_project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "archived"
}

### Admin archives a project (checks for in-progress tasks first)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/projects/{{acme_project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "archived"
}

### Fail: reopen an archived project
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/projects/{{acme_project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active"
}

### ---
### Task controllers (validate_task, enforce_task_rules, notify_assignee)
### ---

### Create a task (auto-fills created_by, defaults priority to "medium")
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project_id": "{{acme_active_project_id}}",
  "title": "Design homepage mockups"
}

### Create a task with explicit assignment
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project_id": "{{acme_active_project_id}}",
  "title": "Implement auth flow",
  "priority": "high",
  "assigned_to": "{{acme_user_id}}"
}

### Fail: create task in archived project
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project_id": "{{acme_archived_project_id}}",
  "title": "This should fail"
}

### Fail: assign task to user in different org
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project_id": "{{acme_active_project_id}}",
  "title": "Cross-org assignment",
  "assigned_to": "{{widgets_user_id}}"
}

### Move task to in_progress (valid: todo -> in_progress)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks/{{task_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress"
}

### Fail: skip status (todo -> done)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks/{{task_id_todo}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

### Mark task as done (only assignee or admin — adds X-Completed-By header)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks/{{task_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "done"
}

### Fail: reassign a completed task
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks/{{task_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assigned_to": "{{another_user_id}}"
}

### Reassign an in-progress task (triggers X-Notification header)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/v1/tasks/{{task_id_in_progress}}
Authorization: Bearer {{acme_admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assigned_to": "{{acme_user_id}}"
}

### ---
### Tenant B (Widgets Inc) operations
### ---

### Create a project for Widgets Inc
POST http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{widgets_member_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Inventory System"
}

### Try to get Acme's project — returns 404 (tenant isolation)
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/projects/{{acme_project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{widgets_member_token}}

### ---
### super_admin — sees all tenants
### ---

### List all projects across all organizations
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}

### Can read any tenant's specific project
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/projects/{{acme_project_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{super_admin_token}}
